## Deliverables

### 1. Row-Level Security ✅
- `apps/api/internal/db/migrations/010_rls_policies.sql` — 8 tables with RLS policies
- Functions: `current_tenant_id()`, `current_user_id()`, `current_user_is_admin()`
- Role: `bypass_rls` with BYPASSRLS privilege
- Policies: SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE per table
- Indexes for RLS performance

### 2. Connection Pooling ✅
- `apps/api/internal/db/pool.go` — Full pool implementation
- Config: MaxOpen=25, MaxIdle=10, MaxLifetime=30min
- Health checks every 5 minutes
- Prometheus metrics: open, in-use, idle connections
- User context setter for RLS
- Transaction wrapper

### 3. Seed Data ✅
- `apps/api/internal/db/seeds/seed_004_test_data.sql`
- 50 users, 200 hosts, 500 credentials, 1000 sessions, 10000 audit logs
- 20 host groups, 50 shared credentials, 100 user devices
- Realistic data with proper distributions

### 4. Input Validation ✅
- `apps/api/internal/api/validators/validators.go`
- Email, IP, Port, Hostname, SSH key, Password strength
- Sanitization: SQL injection, XSS, command injection
- UUID, Tag validation

### 5. Rate Limiting ✅
- `apps/api/internal/middleware/rate_limit.go`
- Token bucket algorithm
- Per-endpoint, per-user, per-IP limits
- Strict auth rate limiting (5/min)
- Prometheus metrics
- Cleanup for stale entries

### 6. Tests ✅
- `apps/api/tests/rls_test.go` — 5 test cases
- `apps/api/tests/validation_test.go` — 10 test cases
- `apps/api/tests/rate_limit_test.go` — 8 test cases

